## Hints for Future Agents
- nox merges its env dict over os.environ, so job-level GITHUB_ENV vars like
  WEAVE_CLICKHOUSE_BINARY flow through to pytest without noxfile changes.
- While PR2 is the tip, every trace-tests job runs THREE test steps (sqlite,
  docker CH, local CH) — slower than master by design; PR3 removes one.
- Windows jobs are sqlite-only; the backend is POSIX-only by construction.

## Codebase Discoveries
- nightly-tests.yaml is schedule/dispatch-only: a PR cannot exercise it. Its
  edits are validated by actionlint + sharing step shapes with test.yaml.

